# Mission System Modding & Extensibility Hooks

## Modding Goals
- Allow new missions, objectives, and rewards to be defined via data or code
- Support mission scripting (triggers, conditions, rewards)
- Enable mission packs and community content

## Hooks & Extension Points
- Mission data loader: accepts external JSON/TS files
- Objective handler registry: add new objective types
- Trigger/event system: allow custom mission logic
- Reward handler registry: add new reward types

## Example: Adding a Custom Objective
- Register new objective type with handler function
- Reference in mission data

